  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oven to 300°F (150°C).",
    "2. In a large Dutch oven, brown the beef over medium-high heat.",
    "3. Add the chopped onion and cook until softened.",
    "4. Add the chopped fennel and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "5. Add the carrots and potatoes, and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "6. Add the beef broth and water, and bring to a boil.",
    "7. Cover the pot and transfer it to the preheated oven.",
    "8. Bake for 2 1/2 hours, or until the meat is tender.",
    "9. Stir in the cubed bread.",
    "10. Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley."
